Building
========

- debug version

  $ CXXFLAGS="-fPIC -Wall" \
	NVCCFLAGS="-Xcompiler -fPIC -Xptxas -v --host-compilation=c" \
	cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=RelWithDebInfo .
  $ make


- release version

  $ CXXFLAGS="-fPIC -Wall" \
	NVCCFLAGS="-Xcompiler -fPIC -Xptxas -v --host-compilation=c" \
	cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release .
  $ make

